    <item>
      <title>欧盟向乌克兰提供 350 亿欧元贷款计划，贷款对象为俄罗斯资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/eu-advances-35-billion-ukraine-loan-plan-tied-to-russian-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟初步批准向乌克兰提供高达 350 亿欧元（383 亿美元）的不可偿还贷款，贷款由俄罗斯央行冻结的资产作为担保，以支持乌克兰的战争努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/eu-advances-35-billion-ukraine-loan-plan-tied-to-russian-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 16:15:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
